modeDutyCycleControl 

Demand is signed 16bit 0.16fixedPt. 7FFF is fullfor. 8000 is fullRev.

modePosControl 

Demand 24bit position.

modeSpeedControl 

Demand is 24 bit speed.

modeCurrentControl 

Demand is 24 bit current.

modeSlaveFollower 

Demand is the can node to follow.

modeMotionProfile 

Demand is unused,could be used in future. Control6 has everything we want.
